sentences:
" Dirty Diana " is a song by American artist Michael Jackson .
It is the ninth track on Jackson 's seventh studio album , Bad .
The song was released by Epic Records on April 18 , 1988 as the fifth single from the album .
It presents a harder rock sound similar to " Beat It " from Thriller ( 1982 ) and a guitar solo played by Steve Stevens .
" Dirty Diana " was written and co - produced by Jackson , and produced by Quincy Jones .
The song 's lyrics pertain to groupies .
" Dirty Diana " has a moderate tempo and is played in the key of G minor .
" Dirty Diana " received mixed reviews from contemporary music critics , but was a commercial success worldwide in 1988 , charting at No .
1 on the United States Billboard Hot 100 .
The song also charted within the top ten in multiple countries , including the United Kingdom , France , Italy , and New Zealand .
In 2009 , after Jackson 's death in June , the song re - entered charts , mainly due to digital download sales .
A music video for " Dirty Diana " was filmed in front of a live audience and released in 1988 .
